pageContext.claim: “So now Crooked Hillary is at it again! She is calling Congresswoman Tulsi Gabbard ‘a Russian favorite,’ and Jill Stein ‘a Russian asset.’ As you may have heard, I was called a big Russia lover also (actually, I do like Russian people. I like all people!). Hillary’s gone Crazy!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump minimizes his 2016 campaign's contacts with Russians by comparing himself to Gabbard and Stein. Special counsel Robert S. Mueller III found that the Trump campaign was aware of and welcomed help from Russia, but there was not enough evidence for conspiracy charges.
